end']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/do-you-overstand.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/overstand.jpg" alt="Do You Overstand?! / Soulphiction" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/do-you-overstand.php">Do You Overstand?!<br />Soulphiction</a></h4><p>ファンキーなビートとジャズを感じさせる音作りが中心の音楽です。ジャズと言っても夜を連想させるような音楽ではなく、BGMとしてどんな時間に書けることも可能です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00114XRBS?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00114XRBS" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Do You Overstand?!-Soulphiction']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fdo-you-overstand%252Fid277020831%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Do You Overstand?!-Soulphiction']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/the-long-road.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/longload.jpg" alt="The Long Road / Anomaly" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/the-long-road.php">The Long Road<br />Anomaly</a></h4><p>アコースティックな質感を持ったエレクトロニカです。明るいポップな楽曲が多いので憂鬱な気分なときに仕事に集中させてくれる音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000U5HX1O?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000U5HX1O" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'The Long Road-Anomaly']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthe-long-road%252Fid119179169%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'The Long Road-Anomaly']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/speak.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/speak.jpg" alt="Speak / Michael Olatuja" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/speak.php">Speak<br />Michael Olatuja</a></h4><p>オフィスをカフェやホテルに生まれ変わったような雰囲気に買えてくれる作品です。R&B、ソウルが好きな方にはおすすめの1枚です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002C39T96?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002C39T96" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Speak-Michael Olatuja']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fspeak%252Fid320902439%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Speak-Michael Olatuja']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/tradition-in-transition.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/tradition.jpg" alt="Tradition In Transition / Quantic and His Combo Barbaro" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/tradition-in-transition.php">Tradition In Transition<br />Quantic and His Combo Barbaro</a></h4><p>ノリのよいアフリカン・グルーヴがとても心地よい作品です。これが作業中のBGMによく合います。試してみる価値はあると思います。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002BAW8D4?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002BAW8D4" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Tradition In Transition-Quantic and His Combo Barbaro']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Ftradition-in-transition%252Fid320383994%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Tradition In Transition-Quantic and His Combo Barbaro']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/crooks-lovers.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/crooksandlovers.jpg" alt="Crooks & Lovers / Mount Kimbie" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/crooks-lovers.php">Crooks & Lovers<br />Mount Kimbie</a></h4><p>重めの音楽ですが、音が詰め込まれていないので気軽な気持ちで聴ける音楽です。ゆったりとしているので騒がしくて作業に集中できないといったこともありません。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003OCE0VQ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003OCE0VQ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Crooks & Lovers-Mount Kimbie']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fcrooks-lovers%252Fid376518884%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Crooks & Lovers-Mount Kimbie']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/play-with-the-changes.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/kodanb.jpg" alt="Play With the Changes / 4hero" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/play-with-the-changes.php">Play With the Changes<br />4hero</a></h4><p>作業のピッチを上げたいときに本作品はおすすめです。良質なクラブサウンドで気持ちを穏やかに、そして集中力を高めてくれる音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000LZ53VU?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000LZ53VU" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Play With the Changes-4hero']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fplay-with-the-changes%252Fid211084369%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Play With the Changes-4hero']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

